Definition: a measure of someone's weight in relation to height
Example: to calculate one's BMI, multiply one's weight in pounds and divide that by the square of one's height in inches; overweight is a BMI greater than 25; obese is a BMI greater than 30
Synonyms: BMI, index, a, measure, of, someone, s, weight, in, relation, to, height, calculate, one, multiply, pounds, and, divide, that, by, the, square, inches, overweight, is, greater, than, obese
Category: noun.communication
